    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban euthanasia of healthy pets, create register of owners who have attempted it",
        "additional_details": "Such owners should be banned from owning pets again and be placed on a national register. When an animal is not sick, then euthanasia should not be allowed. Instead of euthanising these pets should be rehomed.",
        "background": "Ban euthanising healthy pets. I personally know of instances where pets have been put to sleep just because they were not wanted, the vets offered to rehome the pet but the owners refused.",
